      "date": "2017-12-08 15:52:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nThis one is less controversed, the clean fix (suspending the copytool until the request times out) lands us straight into LU-10302... Considering this, I believe the patch is landable as is.\n\nFor the record sleeping without any synchronization target is risky and error prone and should not be used in a test.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "2848b4490f2127a673c5b1092df655342c277287",
      "author": {
