        "username": "bougetq"
      },
      "date": "2017-12-13 11:52:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nWith the fix you proposed for LU-10357/LU-10302 I would prefer we take the other approach: suspending the copytool until the request times out.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
